Boys, you know how you've

01:03.230 --> 01:05.357
been hounding us for years

01:05.399 --> 01:06.942
for your own computer?

01:06.984 --> 01:08.485
Well, your mother and

01:06.984 --> 01:08.485
I have arranged a deal

01:08.527 --> 01:10.111
